{"tid":2188115,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"做首相太忙沒空創作 安倍晉三辭職後 <涼宮春日> 系列時隔９年再出新作","createTime":"2020-09-04T04:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T05:20:33.000Z","uid":253829,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0cfbcd3a297505528e65692580699c464dac3e9e","tid":2188115,"uid":253829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:54:50.000Z","msg":"曾經為日本宅宅文化投下震撼彈的《涼宮春日》系列小說最近宣布即將推出最新一集，這可是時隔９年以上的新書，當然讓粉絲們興奮不已！與此同時網路上竟然出現了原作者谷川流就是日本總理安倍晉三的臆測！？原因就在於《涼宮春日》系列上一集是在2011年出版，而安倍晉三是在隔年再次接任首相。最近安倍晉三剛剛宣布因為健康因素請辭，《涼宮春日》系列馬上就公布了新作，這種巧合立刻讓網友們腦洞大開了～～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/23/59/qJeapaaYl6OXrqU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F23%2F59%2FqJeapaaYl6OXrqU.jpg&h=549d9003&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/23/59/qJeapaaYl6OXrqY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F23%2F59%2FqJeapaaYl6OXrqY.jpg&h=0332854c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這個星期一（8月31日），《涼宮春日》系列新作《涼宮春日的直觀》突然宣布將在11月發售，馬上成為日本宅宅們的話題焦點。畢竟這個系列在2003年出版第一集，並且在2006年經由京阿尼之手動畫化之後引爆熱烈反響，成為許多宅宅的入坑作品，在日本輕小說史與動畫史上都佔有重要地位&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/23/59/qJeapaaYl6OXrqc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F23%2F59%2FqJeapaaYl6OXrqc.jpg&h=173fcaf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過《涼宮春日》系列新書出版的消息，卻意外扯上日本另一個進行中的重大事件&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/23/59/qJeapaaYl6OXrqg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F23%2F59%2FqJeapaaYl6OXrqg.jpg&h=9375c403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為什麼這兩件事情會扯在一起呢？這就要從以下的時間軸看起了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n2006年5月1日：《涼宮春日的憤慨》出版<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/23/59/qJeapaaZj5_dqqQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F23%2F59%2FqJeapaaZj5_dqqQ.jpg&h=41fd5cdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2006年9月26日：安倍晉三第一次組閣<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/23/59/qJeapaaYl6OXrqk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F23%2F59%2FqJeapaaYl6OXrqk.jpg&h=c4dad14c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2007年4月1日：《涼宮春日的分裂》出版<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/23/59/qJeapaaYl6OXrqo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F23%2F59%2FqJeapaaYl6OXrqo.jpg&h=4090dfb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2007年9月26日：安倍晉三以身體不適為由內閣總辭<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/23/59/qJeapaaYl6OXr6SX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F23%2F59%2FqJeapaaYl6OXr6SX.jpg&h=233175b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2011年5月25日：《涼宮春日的驚愕》前後集同時發售<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/23/59/qJeapaaYl6OXrqs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F23%2F59%2FqJeapaaYl6OXrqs.jpg&h=6b84fbd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/23/59/qJeapaaYl6OXr6w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F23%2F59%2FqJeapaaYl6OXr6w.jpg&h=553d9be6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2012年12月26日：安倍晉三再次組閣直到現在<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/23/59/qJeapaaYl6OXr6SY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F23%2F59%2FqJeapaaYl6OXr6SY.jpg&h=ef9b752d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n接著就是等到安倍晉三最近宣布辭職，《涼宮春日》系列才時隔９年以上再次推出新書，於是日本網友之間立刻流傳起谷川流是安倍晉三論（谷川流安倍晋三說），聲稱《涼宮春日》系列作者谷川流根本就是安倍晉三的筆名！<br />\n<br />\n「《涼宮春日》在安倍政權期間都沒出新書吧？然後安倍宣布辭職以後馬上就宣布出新作了，換句話說谷川流＝安倍晉三有很高的可能性。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/23/59/qJeapaaYl6OXr6SZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F23%2F59%2FqJeapaaYl6OXr6SZ.jpg&h=611472ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「2011年《涼宮春日》最後出書，<br />\n2012年安倍晉三成為黨主席，<br />\n2020年8月安倍首相辭職，<br />\n2020年11月《涼宮春日》時隔９年半出新書。<br />\n谷川流就是安倍晉三的推論讓我笑了。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/23/59/qJeapaaYl6OXr6Sa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F23%2F59%2FqJeapaaYl6OXr6Sa.jpg&h=b9b33de5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「谷川流就是安倍晉三的推論，從外星人長門有希（Yuki）跟鳩山由紀夫（Yukio）的共通之處，以及古泉＝小泉的種種跡象都增添了可信度。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/23/59/qJeapaaYl6OXr6Sb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F23%2F59%2FqJeapaaYl6OXr6Sb.jpg&h=373c3a06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「谷川流就是安倍晉三的推論：<br />\n《涼宮春日》時隔９年半出新書&rarr;因為當總理很忙<br />\n『我對普通人類沒興趣』&rarr;所以想當總理<br />\n長門有希&rarr;安倍晉三的選區有個長門市。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/23/59/qJeapaaYl6OXr6Sc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F23%2F59%2FqJeapaaYl6OXr6Sc.jpg&h=fb963a98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「關於谷川流就是安倍晉三的推論啊，《憤慨》發售之後第一次組閣導致連載速度下滑，參議院選舉前發售《分裂》卻讓續篇的《驚愕》隔了４年才出，這也可以作為可靠的證據了。（才怪）」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/23/59/qJeapaaYl6OXr6Sd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F23%2F59%2FqJeapaaYl6OXr6Sd.jpg&h=f1533381&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「谷川流就是安倍晉三的推論讓我笑了，所以涼宮春日的原型是安倍昭惠嗎&hellip;&hellip;？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/23/59/qJeapaaYl6OXr6Se.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F23%2F59%2FqJeapaaYl6OXr6Se.jpg&h=3df9331f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82ea93477c59532c64bed251702287939adb91b0","tid":2188115,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:55:45.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418d401e7bdcc3f91e549586868497bafd3ad24d","tid":2188115,"uid":32380,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:57:46.000Z","msg":"谷川流個<span class=\"red\">川</span>打橫寫就係<span class=\"red\">三</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6238107e7563a6f5d15701bf85a0de510aa58181","tid":2188115,"uid":279981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:58:09.000Z","msg":"真心呢套野有咩咁吸引？ <br />\n純好奇求賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d6377ee218988154dd0bc1d4a77b1166fc0dc1","tid":2188115,"uid":221601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:58:31.000Z","msg":"估唔到個阿伯咁有想象力"},{"pid":"a5327fce97db8b084f3acf4c1867988eb6a53250","tid":2188115,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:59:34.000Z","msg":"中二病<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef5b0de1c693b64b9fdef3a345c493a0df669a0","tid":2188115,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:10:30.000Z","msg":"睇下最近有邊個風化犯出冊好過啦"},{"pid":"81719cc628dda059180c0661a2e17da920051163","tid":2188115,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6238107e7563a6f5d15701bf85a0de510aa58181","tid":2188115,"uid":279981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:58:09.000Z","msg":"真心呢套野有咩咁吸引？ <br />\n純好奇求賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:18:30.000Z","msg":"劇情黎講當時算新穎<br />\n加上京阿尼幫佢發揚光大"},{"pid":"d8ddb9e124d13415d76ca000520dfb02ffb279aa","tid":2188115,"uid":90601,